#!/usr/bin/env bash
# lsdlc-wiki-ingest — deprecated shim.
#
# The old template-based ingest (group learnings.jsonl by `type` and emit
# flat pages) has been replaced by the LLM-authored fan-out ingest pattern
# implemented in skills/wiki/SKILL.md and triggered automatically by
# /implement and /debug.
#
# Will be removed in a future release.
cat >&2 <<'EOF'
lsdlc-wiki-ingest is deprecated.

The new wiki lives at <repo>/.linear-sdlc/wiki/ (per wiki_scope=repo) and is
maintained by the LLM via the /wiki skill. The old template-based ingest
path has been retired.

To get started:
  /wiki init            — scaffold the wiki in this repo
  /wiki ingest VER-42   — fan-out synthesis for a ticket
  /wiki query "..."     — ask a question against the wiki

Or let /implement and /debug auto-ingest on completion (default behavior).
EOF
exit 0
